{{Top|leg}}
'''Nelhal Industries''' was a company that produced the [[RGB photoreceptor lens]] used by [[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton]] in the design of their [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2-series astromech droids]]. One of that series' most famous units, [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]], was fitted with these lenses, in conjunction with [[Stears Data]] [[multifunctional optical reader]]s.

